The paper discusses a novel interface for accessing knowledge graphs through star-shaped subqueries, which involves processing SPARQL queries with low selectivity. This topic is closely related to database systems (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), deep learning (cs.DL), and semantic web (cs.SI).
